OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,FA judge has agreed the punishment for
OL,7,FBarton House resident Shaban Ali was
OL,8,Ftoo harsh, given the circumstances.
OL,10,FBristol's oldest tower block - Barton
OL,11,FHouse - had to be evacuated in
OL,12,FNovember due to structural safety
OL,13,Fconcerns.
OL,15,FFour months later, Bristol City
OL,16,FCouncil completed fire safety work and
OL,17,Fsurveys, and residents were told they
OL,18,Fcould move back in.
