OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,FShaban Ali was one of the more vocal
OL,7,Fresidents who was impacted. He was
OL,8,Farrested by police in February when
OL,9,Ffire alarms stacked up to be installed
OL,10,Fat the tower block went missing.
OL,12,FThe court heard that in the first week
OL,13,Fof February, Mr Ali went into Barton
OL,14,FHouse and took some of the fire alarms
OL,15,Fthat were stored in a corridor ready
OL,16,Fto be installed, and instead hid them
OL,17,Fin his flat.
OL,19,FHe said it was a "misguided protest"
OL,20,Fagainst the way residents of the tower
OL,21,Fblock had been treated.
