OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,FThe court was told that the sudden
OL,7,Fevacuation back in November led to Mr
OL,8,FAli's severe PTSD, anxiety and
OL,9,Fdepression.
OL,11,FJudge Peter Blair heard the incident
OL,12,Fwas a "lapse of judgement".
OL,14,FThe submission made on behalf of Mr
OL,15,FAli said: "Shaban is a first-time
OL,16,Foffender, has no prior criminal record
OL,17,F- this was an isolated incident rather
OL,18,Fthan a habitual pattern of behaviour.
OL,19,FThis suggests it was a lapse of
OL,20,Fjudgement rather than a reflection of
OL,21,Fhis character.
OL,26,@wD@KOU
