OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,F"The traumatic evacuation from Barton
OL,7,FHouse led to severe PTSD, anxiety, and
OL,8,Fdepression. Shaban was on mirtazapine,
OL,9,Fwhich significantly impacted his
OL,10,Fjudgement and emotional stability at
OL,11,Fthe time of the offence.
OL,13,F"A recent Government watchdog report
OL,14,Fhas uncovered serious failing in
OL,15,FBristol City Council's housing
OL,16,Fservices, validating Shaban's concerns
OL,17,Fand his advocacy for community safety.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
