OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,F"Shaban faced extraordinary mental and
OL,7,Femotional stress from managing his
OL,8,Fmental health issues, providing for
OL,9,Fhis family and campaigning for public
OL,10,Foffice, all while dealing with
OL,11,Fhomelessness after the evacuation.
OL,13,F"The council's ultimatum to either
OL,14,Freturn to Barton House or face
OL,15,Fhomelessness added severe pressure,
OL,16,Fexacerbating Shaban's mental health
OL,17,Fchallenges and contributing to his
OL,18,Factions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
