OL,3,CBarton House: Resident convicted of
OL,4,Ctheft has sentence reduced
OL,6,FAfterwards, Mr Ali thanked all those
OL,7,Fwho had provided character references
OL,8,Fto the court for the hearing.
OL,10,FHe said: "I would wholeheartedly and
OL,11,Fsincerely like to thank the Honourable
OL,12,FJudge Blair and his colleagues for
OL,13,Fhearing my appeal, and also thank you
OL,14,Fto everyone who provided me with
OL,15,Fcharacter references - heartwarming
OL,16,Fwords.
OL,18,F"Finally, a deep, deep apology to
OL,19,Feveryone I let down, especially my
OL,20,Ffamily."
